MBBS in Philippines is one of the best destinations for Indian students to pursue MBBS. Philippines medical college fee is very affordable. All top MCI & WHO approved medical universities in the Philippines follows the US education system.

After completion of MBBS from the Philippines, the students have brighter career opportunities. The medium of teaching is English in the Philippines which breaks the major barrier of communication for Indian students. The best colleges in the Philippines have top-class infrastructure and faculty for the students.

{/* */}

Philippines medical college fees

Philippines MBBS college fees would range anywhere between 12 – 20 lacs. Every year, more than 8000 students take admission in the Philippines Medical colleges/universities because they provide a high quality of education. The cost to complete the MBBS course is reasonable and there is no donation fee in many Philippines Medical Colleges.

Philippines medical colleges offer theoretical as well as practical education which empowers the students to become a successful practitioner. The medicinal course provided to students in Philippines is known as the MD program (Doctor of Medicine). The top medical universities in the Philippines are approved by the MCI and also listed in WHO

Philippines medical college fees structure
